ygData.messageBody:
Depending on your level, you can stay in Paws, and collect mroe staves
for cash, which is probably the most lucrative item available to us
right now. You can go to North Karanas and hunt the wild bugs, lions,
large grizzlies and tough wolves there. You can go to Black Burrow and
see how the other gnolls live, You can take a quick boat ride to Eurd
and see the kerran isle in the Tox forest, or you can go into the
catacombs under Qeynos to fight the filthy lower classes of Qeynos
society.
